{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":null,"text":"这两个女人简直是魔女。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":2,"line_end":4},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"你呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":6,"line_end":6},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_zhen_zhu_jie_mei","text":"她跟你们说了些什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":8,"line_end":8},{"speaker":"char_zeng_zhen","speaker_name":"曾珍","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"她…她问我们是不是处女？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":10,"line_start":10,"line_end":10},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_zeng_zhen","text":"她还说了些什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":14,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":null,"text":"不管怎么样，现在我们总得先找个地方歇下来。","tone":"认真","chapter":10,"line_start":22,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_zhang_long_zi","text":"你到狼山来过？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":34,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_zhang_long_zi","text":"这里的人虽然变了，山势总不会变的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":40,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_lan_lan","speaker_name":"蓝兰","listener":"char_zhang_long_zi","text":"那么你就应该能想得出一个可以让我们歇下来的地方。","tone":"认真","chapter":10,"line_start":44,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_zhang_long_zi","speaker_name":"张聋子","listener":"char_lan_lan","text":"我正在想。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":46,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_sheng_yi_ren","speaker_name":"生意人","listener":null,"text":"各位不必再想，再想也想不出的。但是我却可以带你们去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":50,"line_end":52},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sheng_yi_ren","text":"你是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":62,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_sheng_yi_ren","speaker_name":"生意人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"各位请放心，我只不过是个生意人，不是狼。","tone":"微笑","chapter":10,"line_start":64,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sheng_yi_ren","text":"狼山中也有生意人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":66,"line_end":66},{"speaker":"char_sheng_yi_ren","speaker_name":"生意人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"只有我一个。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":68,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_sheng_yi_ren","speaker_name":"生意人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"因为只有我一个，所以我才能活下去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sheng_yi_ren","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":72,"line_end":72},{"speaker":"char_sheng_yi_ren","speaker_name":"生意人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"因为我能跟那些狼大爷们做各式各样的生意，若是没有我这么一个人，他们有很多事都没有这么方便了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":74,"line_end":76},{"speaker":"char_sheng_yi_ren","speaker_name":"生意人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"那些狼大爷们只会杀人抢钱，不会做生意。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":78,"line_end":78},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sheng_yi_ren","text":"你做的是什么生意？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_sheng_yi_ren","speaker_name":"生意人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"什么样的生意我都做，我替他们收藏，替他们卖出去，我还会替他们找女人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":82,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sheng_yi_ren","text":"这件事的确重要得很。","tone":"调侃","chapter":10,"line_start":86,"line_end":86},{"speaker":"char_sheng_yi_ren","speaker_name":"生意人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"简直比什么事都重要。","tone":"大笑","chapter":10,"line_start":88,"line_end":88},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sheng_yi_ren","text":"所以他们舍不得杀你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":90,"line_end":90},{"speaker":"char_sheng_yi_ren","speaker_name":"生意人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"他们要杀我，只不过像捏死只蚂蚁，捏死只蚂蚁有什么用？","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":92,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sheng_yi_ren","text":"没有用。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":96,"line_end":96},{"speaker":"char_sheng_yi_ren","speaker_name":"生意人","listener":"char_xiao_ma","text":"所以这儿年来我都太平得很。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":98,"line_end":98},{"speaker":"char_xiao_ma","speaker_name":"小马","listener":"char_sheng_yi_ren","text":"你准备带我们到哪里去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":100,"line_end":100}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_lan_lan","name":"蓝兰","alias":["蓝姑娘"],"identity":"江湖女子","faction":"无","role":"companion","archetype":"scholar","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"神秘的江湖女子，财力雄厚，与小马等人同行","personality":{"traits":["果断","精明","冷静","大方","关切"],"speech_style":"直接干练","temperament":"冷静沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_ma","type":"合作者","intensity":50,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"同行伙伴"},{"target":"char_bing_ren","type":"主仆","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"照顾者与被照顾者"},{"target":"char_zhen_zhu_jie_mei","type":"合作者","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"同行者"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[10],"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":2,"line_end":4,"text":"蓝兰才轻轻吐出口气，道：这两个女人简直是魔女。"}]},{"id":"char_xiao_ma","name":"小马","alias":["马"],"identity":"江湖拳师","faction":"无","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"以拳头为武器的江湖侠客，正义感强","personality":{"traits":["豪爽","正直","勇敢","幽默","机敏"],"speech_style":"直来直去","temperament":"热血冲动"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_lan_lan","type":"合作者","intensity":50,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"同行伙伴"},{"target":"char_chang_wu_yi","type":"挚友","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"战友"},{"target":"char_bu_zhan","type":"对手","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"对峙"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[10],"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":6,"line_end":6,"text":"小马笑了笑，道：你呢？"}]},{"id":"char_zeng_zhen","name":"曾珍","alias":["珍珠姐妹"],"identity":"江湖女子","faction":"无","role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"珍珠姐妹之一，与妹妹曾珠一同行动","personali